text: Edward James Dickson (born July 25, 1987 in Inglewood, California) is an American former football tight end. He played for the Baltimore Ravens, Carolina Panthers, and the Seattle Seahawks of the National Football League (NFL). Dickson was drafted out of the University of Oregon by the Baltimore Ravens with the 70th pick in the third round of the 2010 NFL Draft. ==Other websites== *Ed Dickson's NFL player profile Category:1987 births Category:African-American players of American football Category:Living people Category:Baltimore Ravens players Category:Carolina Panthers players Category:Seattle Seahawks players Category:Sportspeople from Inglewood, California Category:American football tight ends
